# Comment: The canonical alias definition - maps an incoming email address to a local username
# role1@mydom1.com:username1

# An alias without a domain part matches more broadly - matches any incoming address with same mailbox part
# role2:username1:username2

# Aliases can map to multiple local usernames
# role3@mydom1.com:username1:username2

#Aliases can also map to fully qualified non-local addresses
# role4@mydom2.com:username3:another@somewhere-else-altogether.com
